attributes.description: Modern Insulators is an arm of the Modern group of Industries and was set up in 1985 in collaboration with Siemens, Germany. Modern Insulators is also India’s largest manufacturer and exporter of porcelain insulators and is closely associated with National and Regional Utilities, Indian Railways, OEMs & EPC companies worldwide.[1]
